  • Classes in com.elte.supplymanagersystem.entities used by com.elte.supplymanagersystem.dtos 
    Class and Description
    Company
    Companies have a Unique name.
    History
    Histories can be assigned to Orders Every History has an Author so only those Users will see the History who works at the same company as the Author With the help of HistoryType, Users can log the process of each order.
    Order
    Orders are the main blocks of the system.
    User
    User Entity Users are used for login and order management A user have: Username, Password, Enabled/Disabled Status A Company: If the User is the director of a Company A User also can have connections with Orders, if the User is assigned to Orders Workplace: Users are assigned to their workplace Users are can be also creators of histories
